{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "internal": "deformmeta", "icon": "SOP/deformmeta", "tags": "capture, character, metaball", "version": null, "namespace": null}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Deform Metaball"], "extent": [0, 20]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Deforms captured points according to metaball deformations."], "extent": [128, 195]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Connect the output of a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/capturemeta", "type": "link", "text": ["Capture Metaball SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/capturemeta.html"}, " to\nthe input of this operator to make Houdini deform the captured skin\ngeometry as the metaballs deform. This node uses the attributes created\nby the Capture Metaball SOP to determine which surfaces are controlled\nby which metaball groups."], "extent": [195, 504]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The density of the metaball where it captured the skin geometry at the\ncapture frame controls how much influence the metaball has when it\ndeforms the skin geometry. This density is multiplied by the weight of\nthe group that metaball is contained in. Group weights are specified by\nthe ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/capturemeta", "type": "link", "text": ["Capture Metaball"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/capturemeta.html"}, " and ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/capturelayerpaint", "type": "link", "text": ["Capture Layer\nPaint"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/capturelayerpaint.html"}, " operators."], "extent": [504, 894]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [894, 906], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Normalize Group Weights"], "extent": [906, 932], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Normalize group weights before performing the deformation."], "extent": [952, 1016]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "normalize"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Deform Normals"], "extent": [1016, 1032], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Deforms the point normals to match the deformation of the\n    points."], "extent": [1032, 1107]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Deform Vector Attributes"], "extent": [1107, 1133], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Deforms the vector attributes to match the deformation of the\n    points."], "extent": [1133, 1212]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Vector Attributes"], "extent": [1212, 1231], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Vector attributes to deform."], "extent": [1231, 1265]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Deform Quaternion Attributes"], "extent": [1265, 1295], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Deforms the quaternion attributes to match the deformation of\n    the points."], "extent": [1295, 1378]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Quaternion Attributes"], "extent": [1378, 1401], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Quaternion (", {"type": "code", "text": ["float[4]"]}, ") attributes to deform."], "extent": [1401, 1452]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Enable Sliding"], "extent": [1452, 1468], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Use this parameter to have points blend their deformation position\n    between a fully deformed position and a rest pose position.  This\n    is primarily meant to be used with metaball fields defined by the\n    ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/muscle", "type": "link", "text": ["Muscle Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/muscle.html"}, ".  The ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rest Anchor"]}, " parameter on\n    this object establishes a rest position relative to the specified\n    rest anchor for each metaball in the muscle geometry.  Note that\n    to generate the effect of muscles sliding under the surface of a\n    character\u2019s skin, the skin must be ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/inflate", "type": "link", "text": ["Inflated"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/inflate.html"}, "\n    over the muscle surface.  The ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/deformmuscle", "type": "link", "text": ["Deform Muscle SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/deformmuscle.html"}, "\n    consolidates these effects in to a single operator."], "extent": [1468, 2158]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Sliding Modifier"], "extent": [2158, 2176], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The amount of sliding to allow during deformation when\n    ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Enable Sliding"]}, " is on. If this\n    parameter is set to zero, then points in the captured geometry\n    stick perfectly to the capturing metaballs during deformation and no\n    sliding occurs. If this parameter is set to one, then points do\n    not stick to the underlying metaballs at all. This parameter may be\n    modified on a per-point basis using the\n    ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/slidemodifierpaint", "type": "link", "text": ["Slide Modifier Paint"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/slidemodifierpaint.html"}, " operation."], "extent": [2176, 2664]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "inputs", "container": true, "type": "inputs_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [2664, 2672], "body": [{"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": ["Captured Geometry"], "extent": [2672, 2692], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["This must be the output of a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/capturemeta", "type": "link", "text": ["Capture Metaball\n    SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/capturemeta.html"}, " (that is, geometry with the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["metaCapture"]}, "\n    point attribute set)."], "extent": [2692, 2842]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "text": "Inputs"}, {"level": 1, "id": "outputs", "container": true, "type": "outputs_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [2842, 2851], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The deformed geometry. The output does not include the\nmetaballs."], "extent": [2851, 2919]}], "text": "Outputs"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [2919, 2928], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/capturemeta", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/capturemeta.html"}], "extent": [2928, 2954]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/capturelayerpaint", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/capturelayerpaint.html"}], "extent": [2954, 2985]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/deformmuscle", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/deformmuscle.html"}], "extent": [2985, 3011]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["Deform Metaball"], "summary": ["Deforms captured points according to metaball deformations."]}